title: Suicide Squad 22 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
This is from the original scanner. I adjusted the resolution and 

compressed the file for easier reading on tablets and ereaders. I 

have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Suicide Squad 22

By:   	Alex Kot, Patrick Zircher, Jason Pearson	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Series:   	Suicide Squad
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	July 10, 2013


An anarchist group has a monstrous plan to rewire the brains of the 

American public, starting in Las Vegas! So it's up to Amanda 

Waller's team to shut them down-but a surprise new squad member 

with a grudge against Deadshot threatens to wreck everything!
